BEST BZA / Privacy Statement / Review Description

The application receives notifications/updates from machines used in our workplace and shares them only with responsible team members who have voluntarily joined our Facebook page. 
The system collects only local, anonymous IDs assigned to users for internal server management. 
These IDs do not contain or reveal any personal information and are used solely for operational purposes. 
No other personal data is required or collected. 
All information remains securely within the company network.
